'''Plasma leeches''' were a widespread [[Species/Legends|species]] of spaceborne parasites. They spent their entire lifecycle attached to the surfaces of [[Starship/Legends|spacecraft]], subsisting on [[Plasma/Legends|plasma]] and similar energy sources that naturally radiated from such craft. Over millennia of space travel, they spread from [[Wol Cabassh/Legends|Wol Cabassh]] to nearly every corner of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]].

Plasma leeches were close biological relatives of the [[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] [[Wol Cabasshite/Legends|Wol Cabasshite]] species.

